      • run

        public void run()
        Main method of the thread. Method iterated through mediums from database. There is a thousand mediums loaded every iteration and all of them are then downloaded to set folder.

      • download

        private void download(Medium m,
                      Downloader d)
        Method downloads given medium (calls method from Downloader). If the medium is a video, url must be refreshed (instagram has time limited urls for video posts).
        Parameters:
        m - Medium to download
        d - Downloader which is used to download
